{"id": "ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 630, "displayName": {"text": "Community Goods", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdGEwYzRaRmw2Y1ZwcWRUUklSRjl0ZWxsV1RuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Really nice place & food. As you can see from the pics.the line gets long so quick so u better come early or they might be sold out quickly. If you wanna try smth different & light, def. Worth the wait / experience. Worth to try it once.\nMatcha is good but lil. Sweet . Eggs sandwich to the point.\nGood for dates too\nSpace inside is super limited so probably you will need to find a spot to eat.\nOverall vibes are nice", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really nice place & food. As you can see from the pics.the line gets long so quick so u better come early or they might be sold out quickly. If you wanna try smth different & light, def. Worth the wait / experience. Worth to try it once.\nMatcha is good but lil. Sweet . Eggs sandwich to the point.\nGood for dates too\nSpace inside is super limited so probably you will need to find a spot to eat.\nOverall vibes are nice", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mostafa farag", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107514996581590880085/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4tliaKpeQ5Yz3exakdVAv8q9h3UyMdovVMAEkQWgwkkLSVQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-23T02:16:12.842227723Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdGEwYzRaRmw2Y1ZwcWRUUklSRjl0ZWxsV1RuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxdGEwYzRaRmw2Y1ZwcWRUUklSRjl0ZWxsV1RuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe1b46efe3d:0xe267b19bc83d9f63"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SFpDMDRTMGR4U1RFdFlscHVhRUZwVkhOM1puYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "The drinks here are hip and tasty, but overpriced. The einspanner was sweet and rich, but quite frankly way too small for the price (or there was way too much ice). My friend got the matcha latte, which was fragrant and definitely a notch above other matcha lattes I've had, but still not worth the premium and queue time.\n\nI probably wouldn't go out of my way for this, but would visit again if I'm in the area. I'm aware the breakfast sliders are incredible here, but haven't tried them yet. Will update review when I do!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The drinks here are hip and tasty, but overpriced. The einspanner was sweet and rich, but quite frankly way too small for the price (or there was way too much ice). My friend got the matcha latte, which was fragrant and definitely a notch above other matcha lattes I've had, but still not worth the premium and queue time.\n\nI probably wouldn't go out of my way for this, but would visit again if I'm in the area. I'm aware the breakfast sliders are incredible here, but haven't tried them yet. Will update review when I do!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112391684107063049159/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW3drrzmkclXCnMjsjZCIGLOWdVafPs2fNi6jthw-8mnUIGBEh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-28T21:15:03.567447499Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SFpDMDRTMGR4U1RFdFlscHVhRUZwVkhOM1puYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SFpDMDRTMGR4U1RFdFlscHVhRUZwVkhOM1puYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe1b46efe3d:0xe267b19bc83d9f63"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKSE5qVkhYM1ZUU2xwdlpVUTBlVTF1TW05TE9VRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Saw the hype on social media so naturally I had to go see what it was all about. The complaints I have about going here is the difficulty in finding parking and the crazy line. The line does move quickly but still waited about 35 minutes on a Monday morning. Inside was really small but it was fast paced and staff was really friendly. Anyway the latte    Einspänner was good but wasn’t anything crazy. But then I tried the Matcha Einspänner and I can confidently say that is hands down the BEST matcha I have ever had in my life. I could drink that everyday for the rest of my life! And then I tried the sliders 🤌. 10/10 sliders would comeback just for those to be honest. Don’t see the long lines getting shorter any time soon but all I can say is I get the hype.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Saw the hype on social media so naturally I had to go see what it was all about. The complaints I have about going here is the difficulty in finding parking and the crazy line. The line does move quickly but still waited about 35 minutes on a Monday morning. Inside was really small but it was fast paced and staff was really friendly. Anyway the latte    Einspänner was good but wasn’t anything crazy. But then I tried the Matcha Einspänner and I can confidently say that is hands down the BEST matcha I have ever had in my life. I could drink that everyday for the rest of my life! And then I tried the sliders 🤌. 10/10 sliders would comeback just for those to be honest. Don’t see the long lines getting shorter any time soon but all I can say is I get the hype.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michael Deaj", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111023607485070845327/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYqZQ8VPqdKRJVT-fRP07Xbv2RfUMk3dBCBONlS4_Pk2lhjw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-21T06:52:10.569751578Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKSE5qVkhYM1ZUU2xwdlpVUTBlVTF1TW05TE9VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKSE5qVkhYM1ZUU2xwdlpVUTBlVTF1TW05TE9VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe1b46efe3d:0xe267b19bc83d9f63"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWdFdVRkxWM28wWmkxV2FrcDBYMjlEUVhkaVgwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Absolutely worth all the hype it gets!\nWe came at 8:30am on Sunday morning and the line was already super long. We waited about 35 mins and got the sliders with bacon and avocado. 2 matcha’s and they were incredible!!! We’re from the east coast and thought we’ve had some of the best bacon/egg/cheeses but their breakfast sliders definitely surpassed that. Hope they can keep up with the demand. Rotate the employees so they dont burn out and get better seating to accommodate the demand.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Absolutely worth all the hype it gets!\nWe came at 8:30am on Sunday morning and the line was already super long. We waited about 35 mins and got the sliders with bacon and avocado. 2 matcha’s and they were incredible!!! We’re from the east coast and thought we’ve had some of the best bacon/egg/cheeses but their breakfast sliders definitely surpassed that. Hope they can keep up with the demand. Rotate the employees so they dont burn out and get better seating to accommodate the demand.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marsha", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101094665496870298031/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzL98m9H9EW1Daj5RZXIJPkJw2TvQ3IB_xpkU9fyBkXzyZDWHo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-26T07:46:30.294881805Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWdFdVRkxWM28wWmkxV2FrcDBYMjlEUVhkaVgwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWdFdVRkxWM28wWmkxV2FrcDBYMjlEUVhkaVgwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bfe1b46efe3d:0xe267b19bc83d9f63"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPf5utOG_woARY589yJuxZ-I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sa1FURm5UVTFZZG1adWR6RjBOak4yTUhSSlJYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I came on a Tuesday 20 minutes after they opened and there were only 4 people in front of me, which was amazing because I heard this place gets crazy packed. I tried both their matcha latte and Einspänner latte, both definitely lived up to the hype 10/10 and the breakfast sliders were heavenly! Everything came out really quick and they have an outdoor seating area. Overall I think if you can get here early before the crowd it's totally worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came on a Tuesday 20 minutes after they opened and there were only 4 people in front of me, which was amazing because I heard this place gets crazy packed. I tried both their matcha latte and Einspänner latte, both definitely lived up to the hype 10/10 and the breakfast sliders were heavenly! Everything came out really quick and they have an outdoor seating area. Overall I think if you can get here early before the crowd it's totally worth it!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "erin ward", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107112425127283983301/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBvcLvD3dURWmL1f-W9xFkzkKl82_M0mwDHiwbQtP6GNAMQHzz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T23:55:14.640592630Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2